pull_request.title: AuthUser Fetched + API testing shell script Added
pull_request.body:
1 - isTokenValid.ts UPDATED
2 - isTokenValid is used in AuthUserContext using useEffect
3 - NavBar - instead of profile , username is fetched from isTokenValid and used
4 - API-Tester -  a shell script to test api response is Added 

:warning: **Shell Script use bat & curl instead of cat to print response**: Install bat & curl first!

For arch & arch-based distros (can use AUR too) - 
```bash
sudo pacman -S bat curl
```

For debian & debian-based distros (can use nala too) -
```bash
sudo apt install bat curl
```

For Mac -
```brew
brew install bat curl
```
